fr.curie.cd2sbgnml.xmlcdwrappers

Class StyleInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.curie.cd2sbgnml.xmlcdwrappers.StyleInfo

  • public class StyleInfo
extends Object
    Stores the style properties found for some elements For compartments, thickness + outer/2 + inner/2 are fused together into lineWidth. Gradients are not considered. CellDesigner stores colors in argb format, all colors will be stored as lowercase argb hex string, no #.
